Class MessageSendingController

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.vadasz.peter.knockmessenger.Controllers.MessageSendingController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TimeoutHandler.TimeoutListener

    public class MessageSendingController
extends java.lang.Object
implements TimeoutHandler.TimeoutListener
    This class is responsible for controlling the message sending service, error handling, and exceptions. The message sending activity should have az instance of this class.
